      "source_url": null,
      "captured_at": null,
      "author": null,
      "contributor": null,
      "rationale": "Juniper SSG/ScreenOS names DH groups by number (Group 14) while MikroTik RouterOS uses MODP/ECP key-size names (modp2048); the naming mismatch makes it easy to pick different DH groups on the two VPN ends, breaking IKE negotiation. Phase 1 (profile dh-group) and Phase 2 PFS (proposal pfs-group) are configured separately and must both match.",
